act.longTitleEn:
Bill entitled An Act in the public interest, to provide for—
(A) a further restoration, that is a restoration further to that provided in consequence of legislation enacted in 2015, of the remuneration of certain persons in the public service that had been the subject of a reduction effected by legislation enacted in 2009, 2011 or 2013, and for that purpose to repeal or amend certain of the foregoing legislation;
(B) an increase in the amount of pension or other benefits, other than lump sums, (being the amount of pension or other benefits at the level at which they stand fixed, before the passing of this Act, in consequence of legislation enacted in 2010, 2013 or 2015) payable to or in respect of certain persons who were in the public service under an occupational pension scheme or arrangement (by whatever name called) and for that purpose to amend certain of the foregoing legislation;
(C) the repeal of the Financial Emergency Measures in the Public Interest Act 2009;
(D) the payment of an additional superannuation contribution by certain persons in the public service who are members of a public service pension scheme;
(E) the regulation of certain fees and other payments in respect of services rendered to or on behalf of the State;
and to provide for related matters

act.longTitleGa:
Acht do dhéanamh socrú, ar mhaithe le leas an phobail, maidir leis na nithe seo a leanas—
(A) aisiriú breise, is é sin aisiriú de bhreis ar an aisiriú a ndearnadh socrú ina thaobh de dhroim reachtaíocht a achtaíodh in 2015, ar luach saothair daoine áirithe sa tseirbhís phoiblí, arbh ábhar é do laghdú arna dhéanamh le reachtaíocht a achtaíodh in 2009, 2011 nó 2013, agus, chun na críche sin, reachtaíocht áirithe de chuid na reachtaíochta réamhráite a aisghairm nó a leasú;
(B) méadú ar an méid pinsin nó sochar eile, seachas cnapshuimeanna, (arb é atá ann an méid pinsin nó sochar eile ag an leibhéal ar a bhfuil siad arna socrú, roimh an Acht seo a rith, de dhroim reachtaíocht a achtaíodh in 2010, 2013 nó 2015) is iníoctha le daoine áirithe nó i leith daoine áirithe a bhí sa tseirbhís phoiblí faoi scéim pinsean ceirde nó faoi shocrú pinsean ceirde (cibé ainm a thugtar air) agus, chun na críche sin, reachtaíocht áirithe de chuid na reachtaíochta réamhráite a leasú;
(C) an tAcht um Bearta Airgeadais Éigeandála ar Mhaithe le Leas an Phobail, 2009 a aisghairm;
(D) daoine áirithe sa tseirbhís phoiblí is comhaltaí de scéim pinsean seirbhíse poiblí d’íoc ranníoc aoisliúntais breise;
(E) táillí áirithe agus íocaíochtaí áirithe eile, i leith seirbhísí arna dtabhairt don Stát nó thar a cheann, a rialáil;
agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.

